Package: smscollectr
Title: Collect and Process Rain Gauge SMS Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Ousmane", "Ouedraogo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "ousmane@anam.bf")
Description: Ingests, parses, and exports rain gauge SMS messages from Google
    Sheets. Supports incremental reading, CLICOM output, and FTP delivery.
